    "title": "Milky Way",
    "description": "I can only be myself when I'm with you. 🌌⭐\n\nI took this picture on 20th June 2020 with my girlfriend and took me a while to upload it, but finally here it is. 📆🔚\n⠀⠀\nThis was the best picture of the first set of photos I took to the milky way that day. 🖼️\n\nI was amazed and excited when I saw them on the screen of my camera at that moment cause I didn't believe I could do it. 🙌🏻\n\nI guess everyone has the potential to learn and do what they are really passionate about. 💪🏻👨🏻‍🚀",
